Enum Image.ScaleType

    Enclosing class:
    Image

    public static enum Image.ScaleType
extends java.lang.Enum<Image.ScaleType>
    ScaleTypes that can be used when resizing an Image. NN - Nearest Neighbor - Very fast but kind somewhat noticeable scaler (Default). LINER - This is BiLiner, its very fast and descent quality. CUBIC - This is BiCubic, its looks very good in most situations but is a little slower. LANCZOS - This one has the highest Quality but is pretty slow.
